      {
        "type": "email",
        "html": "<p><em>EDITOR’S NOTE: </em>This Daily Poster<em> report is being co-published with </em>Newsweek<em>. Please share <a href=\"https://www.newsweek.com/hillary-clinton-endorsed-candidate-shontel-brown-faces-potential-ethics-probe-1613460\">this link</a> with others.</em></p>"
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "With a week to go before the special primary election for Ohio’s 11th Congressional District, Democratic candidate Shontel Brown may be in hot water.",
